title: Coming Soon: Dear Chelsea Season 2!
itunes:title: Coming Soon: Dear Chelsea Season 2!
description:
Hey fans, just a reminder that we are on a quick hiatus before Season 2, premiering Oct 7. Watch this space! Starting next Thursday, we’ll be dropping some bonus minisodes as we gear up for the new season. You’ll hear from Season 1 callers who took Chelsea’s advice (or didn't!), how things turned out for them, and what happens when the tables are turned and Chelsea answers listener questions about HER life. Stay tuned!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
